These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, game, prince, siglo, oliveros, bongani, bluemaster
City: san-francisco, rome, hannover, new-york, nizza, hamburg, marseilles
 1. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 2. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is the vegafina-smoker##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is the siglo-smoker##1
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is in the middle##1
 7. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the prince-smoker is in an even position##4
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4
10. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
11. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
12. the prince-smoker is the person traveling to nizza##1
13. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
14. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Cigar   | oliveros      | prince      | bongani    | bluemaster    | game | vegafina     | siglo     |
| City   | new-york | nizza | hannover | san-francisco | hamburg   | marseilles | rome |

