.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: polish, thai, egyptian, dutch, pakistani, british, nigerian
There 7 different types of food: cucumber, onion, nectarine, orange, peas, potato, apricot
 1. the egyptian is on the left or right of the thai##3
 2. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the dutch##3
 3. the person eating peas is in an odd position##4
 4. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3
 5. the pakistani is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating potato is the dutch##1
 7. the thai is the person eating peas##1
 8. the british is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 9. the dutch is the person eating potato##1
10. the egyptian is between the person eating potato and the thai##2
11. the british is in the middle##1
12. the person eating apricot is on the far left or far right##3
13. the thai is on the far left or far right##3
14. the nigerian is on the right of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Nationality   | thai   | egyptian | dutch | british   | nigerian | polish | pakistani |
| Food           | peas | cucumber          | potato    | onion | orange     | nectarine      | apricot    |

