.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-3::.
7 different pets are kept: ferret, bird, turtle, hedgehog, guinea-pig, goldfish, hamster
City: new-york, london, boston, miami, colone, berlin, hamburg
 1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
 3. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 4. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
 6. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
 9. the person traveling to london is the owner of the ferret##1
10. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to berlin is the owner of the hamster##1
12. the person traveling to colone is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| Pet   | hedgehog        | bird  | goldfish | turtle | guinea-pig           | hamster           | ferret  |
| City    | new-york | miami | hamburg   | boston    | colone | berlin | london |

