.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-4::.
There 7 different types of food: garlic, pepper, apricot, nectarine, corn, cranberry, potato
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, june, july, may, august, november, march
 1. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person eating garlic##3
 2. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
 6. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
 9. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
11. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
12. the person eating apricot is on the far left##1
13. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4      |      5       |      6      |      7      |
| Food   | apricot | cranberry    | nectarine | pepper | corn      | garlic | potato |
| Birthday     | march  | september | may   | july  | november | august     | june    |

