 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person driving the roller and the person who's birthday is in march##2
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4   |    5    |       6       |      7      |
| Birthday   | august     | march   | december      | july | january    | october | february |
| Transport       | motorbike | ship | trike | roller  | subway | boat     | quad-bike    |

