.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-19::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, oliveros, pall-mall, game, chaman, bluemaster, tiparillo
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: musical, drama, western, spy, family, action, documentary
 1. the oliveros-smoker is the person watching action movies##1
 2. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 3. the person watching family movies is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 5. the person watching family movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
 7. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
 8. the chaman-smoker is the person watching western movies##1
 9. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
10. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
11. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
12. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
13. the person watching family movies is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
14. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |     5     |    6    |    7    |
| Cigar          | game  | oliveros | vegafina     | tiparillo  | pall-mall | bluemaster    | chaman  |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | action  | musical | family | drama | documentary | western |

