.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: august, september, february, june, april, november, january
The people have 7 different hobbies: sudoku, fishing, magic-tricks, chess, skydiving, reading, filmmaking
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |   5    |      6      |    7     |
| Birthday          | november   | february | january | august | april | september | june |
| Hobby   | skydiving | filmmaking      | reading     | magic-tricks  | chess | sudoku         | fishing    |

 